track_notes: We climbed Le Donon, returned to car / picnic place for lunch and then climbed Kohlberg. The plan was then to activate Petite Donon after that, however there was a thunderstorm so Petite Donon was left for another day. The final 200m climb up to Kohlerg passed among young trees, there was no path. Prior to that the track was overgrown for around 400m but was quite passable.
track_title: Kohlberg VO-092 and Le Donon VO-023 as one walk

track_notes:
Difficult, rocky ,steep ... certainly gives you the idea that you climbed a mountain ;-)
More info and pictures on my blog
